languages.text: "Ты все еще с {mf|ним|ней}, кузина?" {n}Голос Маражая становится издевательски-приторным.{/n} "Как поживают твои поиски утраченного семейства? Или служба на побегушках у мон-кай теперь занимает все твои помыслы и время?"

languages.text: « Vous êtes toujours ensemble, cousine ? » {n}La voix de Marazhai est d'un sarcasme débordant.{/n} « Comment se passent les recherches de votre famille disparue ? Remarquez, être à la botte d'un mon-keigh vous prend peut-être tout votre temps... non ? »

languages.text: “你还和{mf|他|她}厮混在一起吗，我的表妹？”{n}玛拉斋愉悦地嘲弄道。{/n}“你寻找失踪家人的进展如何？还是说，你甘愿把你的思想与时间全花在猴子身上，任由猴子摆布？”
languages.original_text: "You are still with {mf|him|her}, cousin?" {n}Marazhai's voice is dripping with saccharine mockery.{/n} "How fares your search for your lost family? Or is being at a mon-keigh's beck and call occupying all your thoughts and time?"

traits.locale_text: “你还和{mf|他|她}厮混在一起吗，我的族人？”{n}玛拉斋愉悦地嘲弄道。{/n}“你寻找失踪家人的进展如何？还是说，你甘愿把你的思想与时间全花在猴子身上，任由猴子摆布？”

languages.text: "Ihr seid noch bei {mf|ihm|ihr}, Cousine?" {n}Marazhais Stimme trieft vor süßlichem Hohn.{/n} "Was macht die Suche nach Eurer verlorenen Familie? Oder beansprucht es all Eure Gedanken und Eure Zeit, einem Chem-Pan-Sey zu gehorchen?"
languages.original_text: "You are still with {mf|him|her}, cousin?" {n}Marazhai's voice is dripping with saccharine mockery.{/n} "How fares your search for your lost family? Or is being at a mon-keigh's beck and call occupying all your thoughts and time?"

traits.locale_text: "Ihr seid noch bei {mf|ihm|ihr}?" {n}Marazhais Stimme trieft förmlich vor süßlichem Hohn.{/n} "Wie läuft die Suche nach Eurer verlorenen Familie? Oder beansprucht es all Eure Gedanken und Eure Zeit, einem Chem-Pan-Sey zu gehorchen?"

languages.text: «¿Aún sigues con {mf|él|ella}, prima?». {n}Marazhai pronuncia sus palabras con un tono exageradamente mordaz.{/n} «¿Cómo va la búsqueda de tus familiares? ¿O estar a merced de {mf|un|una} mon-keigh no te permite centrarte en tus asuntos?».
languages.original_text: "You are still with {mf|him|her}, cousin?" {n}Marazhai's voice is dripping with saccharine mockery.{/n} "How fares your search for your lost family? Or is being at a mon-keigh's beck and call occupying all your thoughts and time?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Aún sigues con {mf|él|ella}?». {n}Marazhai pronuncia sus palabras con un tono exageradamente mordaz.{/n} «¿Cómo va la búsqueda de tus familiares? ¿O estar a merced de {mf|un|una} mon-keigh no te permite centrarte en tus asuntos?».

languages.text: 「まだソイツと行動しているのか、いとこ殿？」{n}マラズハイの口から甘ったるい冷笑がこぼれる。{/n}「行方知れずの家族の捜索はどうした？それともモン＝ケイに手懐けられて、思考も時間も奪われてしまったか？」
languages.original_text: "You are still with {mf|him|her}, cousin?" {n}Marazhai's voice is dripping with saccharine mockery.{/n} "How fares your search for your lost family? Or is being at a mon-keigh's beck and call occupying all your thoughts and time?"

traits.locale_text: 「まだソイツと行動しているのか、いとこ殿？」{n}マラズハイの口から甘ったるい冷笑がこぼれる。{/n}「行方知れずの家族の捜索はどうした？それともモン＝ケイに手懐けられて、思考も時間も奪われてしまったか？」

languages.text: "Hâlâ bunun yanında mısın kuzen?" {n}Marazhai'ın sesinden alaycılık akıyor.{/n} "Kaybettiğin aileni arama işi nasıl gidiyor? Yoksa tüm vaktini, bir mon-keigh'in emrine amade olarak mı geçiriyorsun?"
languages.original_text: "You are still with {mf|him|her}, cousin?" {n}Marazhai's voice is dripping with saccharine mockery.{/n} "How fares your search for your lost family? Or is being at a mon-keigh's beck and call occupying all your thoughts and time?"
